It was the Luclin expansion that gave us the necessary focus items and AA's to make Pet Canni effective and allow us to have a really good long term DPS in a staggered pull camp.  However, it wasn't until PoP was released and people saw the huge bang of FBoT that the perception of Mages as good Long Term DPS started catching on.  
<br />

